locality: Kuruman. Just outside of Molopo Nature Reserve
Mulili Forest. Basal slope of escarpment. Woodland of acacia trees 8-12 m tall over thickets 3-5 m high.
Kaapmuiden, Marloth Park, Tree House, cnr. Njala & Civet streets.
E of Nelspruit, Uitkyk, along gravel road near gate to 'Sunset Creek'.
Along road C16 from Koes to Keetmanshoop
